This thesis demonstrates that a seemingly metaphysical question can be given precise mathematical meaning within set theory and coalgebra. The collaboration among AI systems and a human researcher has produced a synthesis that is both mathematically rich and conceptually deep. We hope this work inspires further investigations into the foundational question of why there is something rather than nothing, and how self‑reference might be the key to reality.

